00:01:26.234 --> 00:01:26.900
I'm a black man.

00:01:26.900 --> 00:01:27.380
I'm a gay man.

00:01:27.380 --> 00:01:28.020
I'm a veteran.

00:01:28.020 --> 00:01:30.870
I'm a lot of different things.

00:01:30.870 --> 00:01:34.490
And I won't bore you with
