00:01:37.867 --> 00:01:39.200
on the Twitter bio and all that.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.339
So I hope you guys like
look me up, and follow me,

00:01:41.339 --> 00:01:42.380
and all that other stuff.

00:01:42.380 --> 00:01:44.280
JIMMY PEARSON: Yeah, and
actually while we're at it,

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:46.071
I should say there are
